<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="24r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l13"><expan>Meıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> <expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu ſand Sebolt ʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_48_r1l14">Erſamer lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freẅnd vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Sebolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l15">Pfıncʒıng vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeır bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Sıg<ex>mund</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc künıg ʒu Speyr <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l17">nu <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan> <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / Dıe <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns wol geſagt vvıe Jr Jn für = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l18">derlıch vnd <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeyt / des wır ewch <expan>fleıſʒıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l19">Denn wır <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> wie <expan>derſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römıſch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l20">künıg den Reyn abſey . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅch <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> daʒ Jr vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l21"><expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet ſo vıl eẅch gefüklıch ſey . wıe er es mıt <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l22"><expan>krönu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> <expan>halt<ex>en</ex></expan> well . Vnd wenn er das lant <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l23">vnd wahin / Vnd ob Jr ıcht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> mer weſt dıe ewch gebüren vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l24">ʒu <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> . vnd wellt vns darinn <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l25">wır eẅch <expan>ſunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawn . das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır vmb eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l26">etc . Denn daʒ es ſeinen <expan>künikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeinen <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gelükl<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l27">vnd wol gıeng das <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> vns ein <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex></expan> frewd vnd troſt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_48_r1l28"><expan>hort<ex>en</ex></expan> das <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> als pıllıch ıſt . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_48" id="24r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Meist<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echt,</ex></expan>
<expan>pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu sand Sebolt zu
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> frewnd und
                            <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Sebolt Pfinczing und
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeir bey
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Sig<ex>mund</ex></expan>, <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> und zu
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. künig, zu Speyr
                                <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> und nu
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan>
<expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> sein, die <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                        wol gesagt, wie ir in fürderlich und <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt, des wir ewch
                                <expan>fleiszikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en,</ex></expan> wie
                            <expan>ders<ex>elbe</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, der römisch künig, den Reyn absey,
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> daz ir uns
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, so vil ewch gefüklich
                        sey, wie er es mit <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>krönu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
<expan>halt<ex>en</ex></expan> well und wenn er das lant
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab und wahin und ob ir icht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> mer west, die ewch gebüren, uns zu
                                <expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan>. Und wellt uns darinn
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> guten <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en,</ex></expan> als wir ewch
                            <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawn. Das
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr
                            <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> etc. Denn daz es seinen
                                <expan>künikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> in <expan>all<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seinen
                                <expan>sach<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gelükl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und wol gieng, das
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> uns ein <expan>besund<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        frewd und trost und <expan>hort<ex>en</ex></expan> das
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, als pillich ist.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
